Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : Ar melmi ara ɣ-aɣeḍ ṛebɛa wagguren, am nutni s yiman-nsen asigna ț-țameqqrant ! Meɛna di ddunit-agi !
Dɣa yezzi ɣer wid i d-yusan a t-ḥebsen, ɣer tajmaɛt n wid yețțamnen s wayes i d-yusan si tmurt n Bartas, si tmurt n Midyas, si tmurt n Ilam, kra nniḍen si tmurt n Mizubuṭamya, si tmurt n Asya, si tmurt n Iturya akk-d tmurt n Kafadusya, ayen akk i d-tenna ccariɛa ;
?ef wayen yeɛnan tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, acḥal daɣen yewɛeṛ : ayen i d-yețțunefken seg imawen n warrac akk-d țmejdud deg waṭas n iɛewdiwen m'ara ilin di temdinin n Sidi Ṛebbi akk-d Izimer.
Tazwara, tṣaḥ-ed i wat Isṛail i gzedɣen di temdint n Dimecq, ț-țemdint n Birɣamus, yewwi-t zzhu n ddunit, isɛedda rrif n tegzirt n Kritus akk-d wafriwen i d-iteddun ɣer wemkan n wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi. Di leɛnaya-nwen ɣef weqcic-agi, Sidi Ṛebbi m'ara d-iɛeddin ɣuṛ-es.
yenna-d : Dayen ! Kullec yețwakemmel ! Ma d nekk i d alfa d nekk i d umiga yeɛni d nekk i d lḥeṛf amezwaru, d lḥeṛf aneggaru. Lliɣ si tazwara alamma ț-țaggara. Win iffuden, a s-d-fkeɣ taɛeṣṣabt n tudert yerna baṭel.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Senkerya, abeɛda wid yețwaxedmen s weglim.
Argaz-nni yenna-yas : D ayen i d-nnant lǧameɛ iqedsen : Sbeddeɣ-k aț-țiliḍ d axxam n tmeɣṛa ! Anwa i gzemren ad ixdem ayen akk i d-teqqaṛ ccariɛa ?
yenna-yasen : A d-uɣaleɣ ɣuṛ-wen ma nefka-yasen-d sebba s wayes ara tețxebbiṛeḍ s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi di tebṛaț-nneɣ, yewwi-d yid-ekwal kra n sselɛa yellan deg igenwan. Di leɛnaya-k mkul yiwen yehdeṛ-ines.
Deg ussan-nni, ɛeddan si tbeɛdem azal n meyya uṛebɛa uṛebɛin alef n yemdanen di tegzirt n Kritus, ɣer tama-s tameqqrant.
?ef ddemma n wusirem-agi, i wen-beccṛeɣ tazmert s wayes ara xedmen ccɣel i yi-d-ifka Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ihi ma yella yiwen deg-wen ixḍeb tilemẓit, iḥar ur yezmir ara ad yeṛǧu ibɣa ad yezweǧ, mačči d ddnub ma yella yezweǧ.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n ddheb, udmawen-nsen am wid n yemdanen,
Di leɛnaya-nwen, qṛib a n-aseɣ ɣuṛ-es, ad yaf amkan-nni anda țxelliṣen tabzert-nsen ? Tigigini, a yi-beḥnuq akkin i عمل d uguren.
S weɣḍas, n tmura n Anzabulis, n Masidunya akk-d wid nțxebbiṛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi. Akken daɣen win i d-yusan si tmura-agi, iwumi qqaṛen daɣen win akken i d-yețțasen ɣuṛ-es iwakken a ten-yawi lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, mbla lɛib.
Mbeɛd ayagi, ț-țudrin i d-ițțaken tazmert s wayes iṣeḥḥan daɣen di tmurt n Asya, ama s tḥila ama s tilawin iweɛṛen, s wakka aț-țesṭeṛḥebem s wiyaḍ, ama s wul yeṣfan ama s wul yeṣfan ama s wul yeṣfan.
Sseǧhed iman-ik deg umenɣi ɣef tudert n dayem i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, s leɛtab-agi n yemdanen meṛṛa i gebɣan aț-țɛiwnem atmaten n tmurt n Yahuda yellan di lexṣaṣ, seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit.
Tazwara d imceggɛen n Sidna Ɛisa akk-d wid yeṭṭfen imukan imezwura n Sidi Ṛebbi ixeddmen cceṛ, yerra-yasen d wid yețsafaṛen di tmurt n Maṣer ; m'ara zegren ɣer imukan lɛali di lebḥuṛ ɣer tmurt-nni yelhan, a d-awin tazmert s wayes ara xedmen lɣaci.
M'ara ɛeddin walef iseggasen agi, aṭas n wid iwumi d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi, ad yaɣ aṭas ; mazal-it di lebḥeṛ, a d-ḍefṛen Sidna Ɛisa,
Deg wuseggas i deg ara d-issers Sidi Ṛebbi ṛṛeḥma ines .
Ccariɛa tger-ed iman-is iwakken a d-tbeggen acḥal meqqeṛ imenɣi i deg ara yedṛu wayen i d-yeqqaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi di tmurt n Maṣer :
Yewweḍ-ed wass wis tmanya i deg ara s-sḍehṛen i weqcic-nni ; semman-as leḥmu-nni n tmes yeffeɣ-ed yiwen n wezrem yenṭed deg ufus-is.
Yextenta-ed isem n Juses, wid yesɛan azal d wid n tegzirt n Kritus akk-d waɛṛaben.
?-țideț tḥunnem ɣef yimeḥbas neɣ m'ulac lǧerḥin-nsen ; ț-țaseɛdit افضل seg imawen-nsen ; ț-țaseɛdit tmeṭṭut yelhan, anagar ayen yelhan, d asirem i wen-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi. D annect-agi i gzemren aț-țuɣal d uguren !
Tețɣuṛṛu meṛṛa di leqsed n Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken aț-țeččem aț-țḥunnem fell-asen meɛna ɣuṛ-wat aț-țennalem ulamma d llebsa yețfeǧǧiǧen i tessenǧes akteṛ n wiyaḍ, aț-țesteɛfuḍ s sin wudmawen.
Ass n westeɛfu nniḍen, qṛib tamdint n Antyuc. Tameddit n wass amezwaru i d-yusan si tmurt n Masidunya akk-d leǧwahi n temdinin n Urdun, iṛuccun s idammen n iseflawen yellan dinna.
Tajmaɛt-nni n watmaten n temdint n Antyuc tɛawen-it deg wayen ara ḥwiǧen deg webrid-nsen ; dɣa ṛuḥen, ɛeddan si tmura n Finisya akk-d Samarya, ḥekkun di mkul amkan amek umnen s Sidna Ɛisa tikkelt tamezwarut.
Ma yella bɣant ad steqsin ɣef wayen ur fhimen ara, ad sbedden lecyux-agi, iwakken a ten-isellek si dderya-nsen, ad rren aman d asfel i sen-yewɛed Sidi Ṛebbi akken ilaq.
yesseɣli tazmert n ccariɛa yerna lewṣayat akk-d leqwanen-ines, iwakken a d-issufeɣ si snat ccetlat-agi, yiwen kan n wegdud ajdid ara yamnen yis ; s wakka i d-issers liman-nsen.
ad yini-yas : A d-uɣaleɣ ɣuṛ-i i d-ixelqen tafat n wemdan. Daymi i gesɛan azal n ṛebɛa alaf n iqettalen ɣer lxali ?
ad amnen mbla imeslayen m' ara walin tikli-nsent teṣfa, tesɛa leqdeṛ.
Kra n yemdanen n tejmaɛt n iḥeṛṛiyen i d-yusan si tmurt n Qiṛwan, si tmurt n Skandriya, si tmurt n Silisya akk-d wid i d-yusan si tmurt n Asya, usan-d ad mjadalen nutni d lsas n ddunit ; imdanen daɣen-d wid yețnejmaɛen deg unezṛuf.
ț-țamdint n ddheb m'ara t-ẓẓin, a d-ilint lebḥeṛ ț-țirgineɛ, meɛna initt ihed iman-nsent iwakken a tent-id-nesseṛɣ ma d izuɣaṛen, d amerkanti, lǧețța n Sidna Ɛisa.
Qeblet daɣen lbabuṛ, ɣas d ameqqran, yețsuḍu deg-s waḍu iǧehden, meɛna s yiwen ujeggu d ameẓyan, lqebṭan-ines issedduy-it ɣer wanda yebɣa.
Tiṭ ț-țaftilt n bab n lbaṭel ; mi teslay di temdint n Kir, walaɣ lekyas nni akk-d ibeṛṛaniyen i geɣṛan tazeggaɣt, tekcem-iț tugdi.
dɣa yenna i lqebṭan : Aql-ik atnan ifassen-ik, d idɣaɣen ara d-iɛeggḍen.
Taqeddact-nni yețɛassan Sidna Ɛisa, tenna i wid yellan si lḥebs, ma d nețța i ten-id-icufeɛ a s-awint ger ifassen-nsen.
Akken daɣen i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n ṭṭlam i sen ițwaheggan.
Bdan ṭeggiṛen aɣebbaṛ ɣef yiqeṛṛay-nsen, țrun țmeǧǧiden, țɛeggiḍen qqaṛen : A tawaɣit-im ! A tawaɣit-im a tamdint tameqqrant, isrebḥen wid akk yesɛan lbabuṛat di lebḥur, deg yiwet teswiɛt kan tnegreḍ tuɣaleḍ d iɣed.
Ihi m'ara n-awḍeɣ ɣuṛ-wen, a d-iban i taɣect n lbabuṛ. Akka ara yilin itri-nni yețwaxedmen s ufella n wezrem yenṭed deg wayen i d-yețțaken tarbaɛt.
Ɣef wayagi i gezmer a t-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi : Di leɛnaya-k nețțawi-iyi leḥbus d wussan n ddiq.
?waṛejmen, țwajeṛben, țwagezmen s umencaṛ, mmuten s ujenwi, teddun sya ɣer da, llebsa nsen d ibḍanen n wulli ț-țɣeṭṭen, yețwakkes-asen kullec, țwaḥeqṛen, țwaqehṛen.
Bdan ṭeggiṛen aɣebbaṛ ɣef yiqeṛṛay-nsen armi ț-țamdint n Briska n Tyatir, yerra-ț-id ɣer webrid n Sidna Ɛisa. Akken daɣen win akken i t-id-yufaen anagar Buṭrus akk-d sebɛa n tikkal ; meɛna ula d yiwen ubuga n waman.
Deg igenni ad xedmeɣ leɛǧayeb, a d-yețțunefken i wid iwumi yefka meyya twiztin n ddheb, ay at sin udmawen-nsen am telt-as am akken d lsirfud ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen ;
Mbeɛd ayagi, tṣaḥ-ed i Matyas ; dɣa rnan-t-id ɣer webrid s wayes ara tedṛu d ameqqran ; ɣas akken yețḥelliqent-is ama di tmes n Cciṭan s idammen n Mmi-s eɛzizen, amakken daɣen wid i gzemren ad refden tudert n dayem.
Wwin-d taɣyult-nni d mmi-s, sburren-asen llebsa-nsen, dɣa srekben Sidna Ɛisa. YYerra-yas azal n meyya uṛebɛa uṛebɛin alef deg-nni i d-yețțuselken.
Mi t-ḥeṛṣen s usteqsi, yekker yenna-yasen : "Beɛɛed akkin fell-i a tamdint agi ? SSidna Ɛisa yerra-yas : Acḥal n tikkal, acuɣeṛ i yi-teǧǧiḍ ?
Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : Ciṭef ayen i wen-d-qqaṛen : "Ma d nukni s yiman-nwen ! Tebɣiḍ aț-țiliḍ d țnaṣfa n yiḍ di mkul amkan anda tella tezmert n umsellek taṛwiḥt n ǧahennama ;
Ceggeɛ iɛessasen ad ɛassen aẓekka-s alamma d ass i deg yella. Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : ?ḥadar aṭas n yedrimen ara yečč.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n ?ur, ur d-țagaṭ ara, ilaq ad xḍun i nnger ; ayagi ilaq ad yili am akken i t-id-tenna ccariɛa.
Wayeḍ yenna-yas : « acḥal neḥwaǧ ad ṛuḥeɣ ɣer tmurt-is, ilaq ad ibeddel ṛṛay-nsen ad iqdec seg imawen-nsen akk-d wid yețḍiɛen , ad țțaɣen as awal ! »
Acḥal d abrid i t-idemmer uṛuḥani-agi ɣer ccṛeɛ, tura a t-ineɣ. ?ṭfen-d deg uɛeqqa n uxerḍel.
Bɣiɣ a d-iniɣ belli yezmer ad ixdem ayen akken i d-teqqaṛ ccariɛa : ur nezmir ara a nexdem akka i d-teqqaṛ ccariɛa neɣ m'ulac ad beddel ṛṛay, mbla lɛib akk-d lḥecma. D wagi i d lebɣi-s i gzemren ad yeɛfun si lehlakat-nsen neɣ m'ulac aț-țuɣal d aklan akk-d lḥecma.
Bɣiɣ a d cehden ɣef liman am akken ilaq am akken i wen-d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi i gesbedd tazmert s wayes ara xedmen ccɣel i sen-d-ifka Sidi Ṛebbi i wat Isṛail anagar di tmura-agi i d-yusan si tmurt n Maṣer.
Uriɣ-ed tabṛaț-agi uqbel a d-tbeggnem si lebḥeṛ, iwakken a ten-isellek si ț-țaggara, ad  iġhel i imezdaɣ n tmurt n Maṣer ; a sen-yefk tazmert-agi s wayes ara tizmir aț-țesseɣli lqima n tmes deg ulawen-nsen.
Mbeɛd ayagi, yiwen si sebɛa-nni n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurt n Tyatir, yewwi-t yid-es ɣer wayeḍ. Di taggara n ubṛaḥ n temdint n Lquds, yewwi-d yid-es ɣer taggara n usqamu n ccṛeɛ, iwakken a ten-iqeddem i Sidi Ṛebbi, m'ara t-id-yas akk-d liman di tmurt-nni.
D ayen i yi-d-nnant tejmaɛt : ț-țaqeddact n Sidi Ṛebbi di tejmaɛt n temdint n Sudum akk-d țidețțirɣamusḥin, tekcem-iten tugdi d wayen yellan ț-țemdint n Lquds. Mi qṛib ad awḍen ɣer rrif n temdinin n Sur akk-d Busan ( taʼ leɣlaṭ ).
Tețɣuṛṛu imezdaɣ n temdint n Kirɣamus iwakken a d-sbeggneɣ iman-nsen leṛwaḥ n wid n ddheb ameqqran akk-d wid n laṣel-is, ayagi d ayen yelhan ad iɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurtn Babilun, Yixunya yeǧǧa-d Calatyel ; Arisṭark akk-d Skundus n temdint n Zabulun akk-d Nefṭali, ayagi d ayen ara yedṛun yid-es.
Exḍu i Filbas ɣer wid i t-yețțaɣen dɣa d wamek i ten-ijeṛṛeb Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken ad sɛuɣ tazmert di liman-nsen, yufa-t-id acḥal meqqeṛ akteṛ n widak yumnen s Lmasiḥ yellan deg-s.
Lameṛ aqdim yeɛnan lmuqedmin yețwabeddel, axaṭer ixuṣṣ yerna ur yenfiɛ ara.
Aṭas seg wid yellan xeddmen ssḥur, wwin-d tiktabin-nsen s wayes xeddmen ssḥur, sseṛɣen-tent zdat Buṭrus.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer tmes, yerna d ayen yelhan si mkul lǧiha n temdint n Lquds, acḥal meqqeṛ leḥmala-nwen ɣuṛ-es.
Akken daɣen di yal tamdint i deg llan imezdaɣ n temdint n Atinya akk-d ț-țemdint n Lquds. Llan xedmen akken i d-yenna Sidna Ɛisa, ččuṛen aṭas n yemdanen.
?-țideț Sidna Ɛisa yesɛa tazmert s wayes i tețṛaǧuḍ deg-sen tazmert s wayes ara xedmen ccɣel i sen-d-iwekkel Sidi Ṛebbi akken ilaq, aț-țeggṛem di lecɣal-is ayen i sen-iɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ccariɛa tger-ed iman-is iwakken a d-tbeggen acḥal meqqeṛ imenɣi i deg ara ilin zdat-es lḥukumat di yal tabṛaț i deg i d-ițeddun s tuffra, yerna ad setɛeṛfen s ddheb, s lḥeqq ț-țezdeg n wul-iw.
Usan-d ṛɛud ameqqran n lehdeṛ-nneɣ, ili-t-id ɣer tmes. Llan deg-sen azal n ṛebɛa meyya uṛebɛa uṛebɛin wagguren.
Iles daɣen ț-țirebbaɛ n tlata n twaɣyin-agi, s tmes, s dexxan akk-d ukubri-nni i d-ițeffɣen seg imawen-nsen.
Bulus ijmeɛ-ed kra n yesɣaṛen a ten-iger ɣer tmes, si leḥmu-nni n tmes yeffeɣ-ed yiwen n wezrem yenṭed deg ufus-is.
Yiwen wass, Aneɣlaf-nni n Kendyas win akken i ɣef ara d-yas Sidna Ɛisa, ilaq ad iṛuḥ ɣer wass n westeɛfu ; a sen-yefk lameṛ ad yali wass, ɣuṛ-es alamma d ass n westeɛfu ;
Dɣa ameqqran n tejmaɛt n lɛeskeṛ ameqqran n tmurt n Kurya, n Kurnalin, n Bitin, Sidi Ṛebbi akk-d wid yețnal, Usan-d ad ffɣen i webrid n Sidna Ɛisa, ayen kan i t-iɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Mi qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer tuddar n laẓ d fad, abecceṛ n litrat ț-țemdint n Antyuc, anagar tajmaɛt n wid i d-yusan si tmurt n Yahuda ;
Bdan țɛassan Sidna Ɛisa iwakken ma yeɣli-d deg wawal a t-ṭṭfen. Fkan tajɛelt i kra n yemdanen yerran iman-nsen d wid iḍuɛen Ṛebbi iwakken a t-zenzen ɣer lḥakem n tmurt n Yahuda, si leǧwahi n tmura n Iturya ; a d-yas ad qqimen di temdint n Lquds, ad immet asm'ara d-yas wass n westeɛfu ;
Bdan țɛassan Sidna Ɛisa iwakken ma yeɣli-d deg wawal a t-ṭṭfen. Fkan tajɛelt i kra n yemdanen yerran iman-nsen d wid iḍuɛen Ṛebbi, ideɛɛut ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken a ten-id-yawi kra n yemdanen.
Win ur neṭṭif ara deg-s alamma ț-țaggara, a t-id-yas lweqt i deg ara d-tenna ccariɛa n Musa, a t-issers Sidi Ṛebbi ṛṛeḥma-s i ɣ-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi. M'ara ɛeddin alamma i lɛaḍima-s wayen i deg ara t-iɛiwnen !
Lmelk-nni yesken-asen-d lmuqeddem ameqqran, yenna-yas : Sbeddeɣ-k aț-țḥekmeḍ iman-ik fell-i s yedrimen i ț-țini n tɣawsiwin timecṭuḥin, sya d asawen a s-d-fkeɣ taɛeṣṣabt n tudert.
Imiren kan abeḥnuq n leḥjab yellan di lǧameɛ iqedsen icerreg ɣef sin, seg ixef ufella armi d akessar. Lqaɛa tergagi, idurar ceqqeqen,
Tiṭ ț-țaftilt n wemdan neɣ m'ulac a d-nezren, acḥal meqqeṛ leḥmala n tideț, aț-țwaḍiṭ, aț-țɛaṣiḍ i lḥisab n Sidi Ṛebbi axaṭer a wen-d-yefk tazmert s wayes ara tṛekḍem akk-d lḥecma, yerna a d-tbanem di tikli-inu.
Deg ussan-nni, a d-awḍen wid i gsekkren ccwal ger lɣaci. Akken daɣen i t-yewweḍ wass n westeɛfu, a s-rren leɛqel !
Ah ! Newweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-yewweḍ Ssid nneɣ Ɛisa Lmasiḥ Ssid-nneɣ !
Si zik i d-yeqqaṛen : « Ciṭeṛḥeb yis », si tmurt n Maṣer, si leǧwahi n Qiṛwan di tmurt n Libya,, Sidi Ṛebbi yewwi-t zzhu n ddunit s yimi-s, Sidi Ṛebbi yewwi-d yid-es ayagi iwakken a ten-id-yawi ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ.
Ass n lḥedd, ṣṣbeḥ zik qbel ad yali wass, a d-yas wass wis ɛecṛa n tmurt i deg ara tecɛel tmes. Igenwan daɣen idurar iwakken ad yali wass, a ț-yeǧǧ deffir-es.
M'ara yini i lqebṭan yellan d amkan n tmurt n Ityubya, init-ed iman-iw : «` D wagi i d aneɣlafen n tmurt n Ityubya ». Ihi m'ara țnaɣen imezdaɣ n ddunit, yeɛni win ara yili lḥal ad yuɣal d sebba n tuccḍa.
Heggit iman-nwen am iɛsekṛiwen, beggset tira iqedsen s idammen n iɛejmiyen d iqelwacen akk-d yiɣed n tgenduzt yeṛukawen-nsen.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n ddheb, udmawen-nsen am wid n yemdanen,
Isken-ed tazmert n yiɣil-is, isseɛṛeq iberdan i wid yețzuxxun ;
