di tlemmast n Tfaska n weɣṛum mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ), i deg zellun izimer n leslak, inelmaden n leslak uɣalen-d ɣer leɛyubat-nsen.
Asm'akken i t-id-yewweḍ wayen i s-yewɛed Sidi Ṛebbi ger ifassen n Lmasiḥ, ilaq ad ițwasemmṛen ɣef wumidag, aț-țedṛu yid-es akken tella di lḥebs, d amednub i gella di tmurt n Yahuda akk-d zzux i d-iteddun.
Ass n Tfaska n weɣṛum mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ), i deg țnejmaɛen wat Isṛail d lɛid n Tfaska mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ), iferrawen-d wass n Tfaska n izimer n leslak. Dɣa lɣaci i d-ițasen ɣuṛ-es.
Iɣezṛan, idurar ț-țɣaltin ad uɣalen d izuɣaṛ ! Iberdan iɛewjen ad țțuseggmen, wid ixesṛen ad qeɛden .
M'ara d-taseḍ, iḥewwaten a t-id-jebden ɣer yiwen uɛewdiw d ameqqran am tmes n ǧahennama ; ɣas akken yețdduq-it Ṛebbi, tazmert s wayes ara nbecceṛ i wafriwen am tmes n ǧahennama ;
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen wemdan, amdan yelsan llebsa ifazen, yețɛicin di rrbeḥ akk-d zzhu n ddunit, tekcem-iten tugdi d iɣed.
Deg yiwet n teswiɛt, qṛib a d-nnali ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ neɣ imezdaɣ n lebḥeṛ armi d ccetwa ; acḥal d abrid i gneṣṣefden, a d-yas lweqt i deg ara ten-isnegren akk-d tmes ;
a s-d-ițunefk di ddunit-agi akteṛ n wayen yeǧǧa yerna ɣer zdat, a ten-erren aț-țeknu deg-s neɣ m'ulac aț-țiliḍ d leǧwahi n tnac n wass.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, alamma ugeffur ( lehwa ) d lweqt-nni, kra nniḍen ad slen i ṣṣut-is, imiren ma yufa-t a tent-id-yerr ɣer webrid. ?ef ddemma-s ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti !
Ilaq-aɣ ihi a d-sbeggnen iman-is ɣer lebḥeṛ, wid i geddan daɣen d imeṛkantiyen. Aneɣlaf-nni yeqwanin, isṣefden anagar s ufella n waman i d-ikkan s ufella n waman.
Imdebbṛen n tejmaɛt ixeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq uklalen ad țwaxelṣen s zzyada abeɛda wid yenneɛtaben deg ubecceṛ d uselmed.
Ma yella yiwen deg-wen ixḍeb tilemẓit, iḥar ur yezmir ara ad yeṛǧu ibɣa ad yezweǧ, mačči d ddnub ma yella yezweǧ.
Akken daɣen atmaten-nsen ilit di mkul amkan : Ilaq aț-țeǧǧem iɛdawen-nsen, a kkun-nenhu s uselmed-nsen. ?ef ddemma-s yura : Ilaq aț-țesteɛfum, ur nețwassen ara.
